  "name": "Morrison COU1 — FDA generic centrifugal pump hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-1 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under VAD conditions. All 13 credibility factors assessed with achievedLevel >= requiredLevel. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed. Full provenance chain documented. Decision: Accepted.",
